# Do NOT commit PDFs or figures (kept out of version control by request).
# The manuscript PDF and regenerated figures are distributed via the Zenodo
# deposit, not the git repository.
*.pdf
figures/*
!figures/.gitkeep

# Regenerated text outputs (tables/, data/processed/) ARE tracked so reviewers
# can see them without running the pipeline. Uncomment to treat as artifacts:
# tables/*.csv
# tables/*.md
# data/processed/
